### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">أَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ إِلَى ٱلطَّيْرِ مُسَخَّرَٰتٍ فِى جَوِّ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مَا يُمْسِكُهُنَّ إِلَّا ٱللَّهُ ۗ إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَـٰتٍ لِّقَوْمٍ يُؤْمِنُونَ</span>

### English

Have they not seen the birds glide in the open sky? None holds them up except Allah. Surely in this are signs for those who believe.